ationship manager at Respondent, who did not notice the altered email addre=
ss used by the threat actor, did not take steps beyond replying to the emai=
l chain to verify that the Issuer did in fact want to issue and liquidate n=
ew shares and then transfer the proceeds to a foreign bank.</p><p style=3D"=
margin: 16px 0;">Over the course of a month, at the direction of what appea=
