arty broker-dealer to sell approximately 3.3 million of those new shares fo=
r about $4.78 million. Respondent transferred all the proceeds to Hong Kong=
-based bank accounts.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Issuer even=
